  "short_description": "Discover the fantasy world filled with danger and awe in the Prologue of Alchemist Adventure! It features an exclusive chapter of the game that allows you to embrace the power of alchemy. Combine various elements, solve puzzles, fight monsters and explore the corridors of the mysterious dungeon.",
