  "detailed_description": "<h1>Available now</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The Prologue of Alchemist Adventure is a unique dungeon that you can try out for free. It allows you to take a close look at all the basic mechanics, craft every possible kind of potion, solve environmental puzzles and fight furious enemies!<br><br>The Prologue also gives players a crack at the Dragon Challenge, a unique boss fight against Crystalis the dragon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/1c0106f06552f2aa50161a82d011f582.avif?t=1646498805\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combine elements and make all kinds of potions</strong></h2>Use the four basic elements (fire, water, air, earth) along with special ingredients to create bombs, elixirs, and sword oils.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/7d2ad5a7c5134b3a4c19b310c7664421.poster.avif?t=1646498805\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/7d2ad5a7c5134b3a4c19b310c7664421.webm?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/7d2ad5a7c5134b3a4c19b310c7664421.mp4?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Transform the world around you</strong></h2>Interact with the environment using alchemy. Raise the water level of a lake, cross a river by creating ice platforms, use the wind to move objects, and create lightning to start an engine!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/b37d311522893d49bf8f9884abdc4563.poster.avif?t=1646498805\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/b37d311522893d49bf8f9884abdc4563.webm?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/b37d311522893d49bf8f9884abdc4563.mp4?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve alchemical puzzles</strong></h2>Combine elements to open chests, make paths, or find hidden objects. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/1171152c45f645c98a0b1a8c6e0a6a77.poster.avif?t=1646498805\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/1171152c45f645c98a0b1a8c6e0a6a77.webm?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/1171152c45f645c98a0b1a8c6e0a6a77.mp4?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight fearsome foes</strong> </h2>Use elements to discover enemies’ weaknesses and try different strategies to defeat them. Large or small, every enemy has its achilles heel, and it's up to you to find and exploit it with your alchemy powers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/2736d90b06cddca2154bdc76bceb9316.poster.avif?t=1646498805\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/2736d90b06cddca2154bdc76bceb9316.webm?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/2736d90b06cddca2154bdc76bceb9316.mp4?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Switch between characters or play co-op</strong></h2>Join the journey as a flying homunculus that can fight, solve puzzles, and collect resources, or play co-op with a friend as Mya and her homunculus.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/d3cf3cd52e391281640d1fcfbb6981e4.poster.avif?t=1646498805\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/d3cf3cd52e391281640d1fcfbb6981e4.webm?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433100/extras/d3cf3cd52e391281640d1fcfbb6981e4.mp4?t=1646498805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
